(Troubleshooting Guide \(Atho\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Status: Alpha documentation snapshot \(2026-03-12\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This guide collects common issues and fixes by area \(network/P2P, APIs/auth, storage/LMDB,) Tj
T*
(mining, Docker, build/tooling\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Most Common Right Now \(Fast Fixes\)) Tj
T*
(- **Nodes won?t start from GUI / start inconsistently**) Tj
T*
(- Cause: stale background processes or PID conflicts.) Tj
T*
(- Fix:) Tj
T*
(- ./.venv/bin/python Src/Main/stop.py --active) Tj
T*
(- ./.venv/bin/python Src/Main/stop.py --all) Tj
T*
(- start again from GUI Node tab or Src/Main/runnode.py.) Tj
T*
(- **GUI says auth/API key issue**) Tj
T*
(- Cause: API key/user/password not set or mismatched between GUI and Api_Keys.json.) Tj
T*
(- Fix:) Tj
T*
(- regenerate key: ./.venv/bin/python Src/Api/auth.py) Tj
T*
(- re-enter values in GUI Settings.) Tj
T*
(- **Falcon/Kyber binary or compile failures**) Tj
T*
(- Cause: missing compiler/toolchain or wrong platform binary.) Tj
T*
(- Fix:) Tj
T*
(- follow compile sections in README.md and Docs/quickstart.md) Tj
T*
(- register Falcon binary:) Tj
T*
(- ./.venv/bin/python Src/Falcon/Falcon/install_platform_binary.py) Tj
T*
(- confirm compiler exists \(clang/gcc/cc\).) Tj
T*
(- **Peer connects but later drops \(Connection refused\)**) Tj
T*
(- Cause: peer process stopped, wrong target port, or service restart timing.) Tj
T*
(- Fix:) Tj
T*
(- verify target node process still running \(stop.py --active\)) Tj
T*
(- verify correct P2P port from Src/Config/NodePorts.json) Tj
T*
(- restart both peers and recheck logs/mainnet/network/network.log.) Tj
T*
(- **Remote peers cannot connect to bootstrap IP**) Tj
T*
(- Cause: bootstrap set to private LAN IP \(192.168.x.x, 10.x.x.x, 172.16-31.x.x\).) Tj
T*
(- Fix:) Tj
T*
(- use public endpoint \(DDNS/public IP + port-forward\) or VPN mesh endpoint \(Tailscale/ZeroTier\).) Tj
T*
(- keep LAN IP only for local-network testing.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Network / P2P) Tj
T*
(- **Peers=0 / no headers:** Check ATHO_BOOTSTRAP and network \(ATHO_NETWORK\) match your seed;) Tj
T*
(ensure P2P port \(default 56000\) is reachable. Clear peers: rm Src/Config/Peers.json and restart) Tj
T*
(with ATHO_RESET_PEERS=1.) Tj
T*
(- **sync_no_headers or tip stuck at 0:** Often a network mismatch or genesis mismatch. Align) Tj
T*
(ATHO_NETWORK across nodes; verify bootstrap points to the right chain.) Tj
T*
(- **Block rejects like 'Transaction' object has no attribute 'get':** Incoming blocks weren?t) Tj
T*
(deserialized to the expected dicts. Ensure all nodes run the same code/version; wipe stale) Tj
T*
(storage if formats changed.) Tj
T*
(- **Port in use:** Pick a free P2P/API port \(ATHO_P2P_PORT, ATHO_FULLNODE_API_PORT,) Tj
T*
(ATHO_MINERNODE_API_PORT\) or let runnode.py auto-assign. On Docker, avoid binding API ports if) Tj
T*
(they conflict; use random host ports.) Tj
T*
(- **Different tips across nodes:** Confirm all nodes point to the same bootstrap seed and) Tj
T*
(network; if a node lags, clear its storage/peers and resync.) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
endobj
