(- **Repeated sync_headers_ok but no progress:** The serving peer may be on a short fork or) Tj
T*
(serving invalid blocks. Point to a trusted seed with the desired tip; stop low-tip peers.) Tj
T*
(- **Genesis mismatch:** Changing genesis content requires all nodes to resync; mixed genesis) Tj
T*
(nodes will reject each other?s chains.) Tj
T*
(- **Many rpc_fail ... short_header / reconnect churn at scale:** Tune peer/network concurrency) Tj
T*
(and backoff to reduce dial storms and socket churn:) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_P2P_RPC_TIMEOUT=2.5 to 4.0 \(lower probe RPC timeout\)) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_PROBE_BATCH_SIZE=16 to 32 and ATHO_PROBE_WORKERS=4 to 12) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_OUTBOUND_MAX_NEW_PER_CYCLE=1 to 3 \(limit new dials per keepalive cycle\)) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_OUTBOUND_RETRY_BASE_SECS=5 and ATHO_OUTBOUND_RETRY_MAX_SECS=300) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_DROPPED_PEER_READD_DELAY_SECS=120 to 300 \(avoid immediate re-add of failing peers\)) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_SYNC_PEERS_PER_CYCLE=3 to 6 \(cap sync fan-out\)) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_P2P_SERVER_CLIENT_WORKERS=32 to 128 \(bound inbound worker pool\)) Tj
T*
(- **Slow block relay on larger responses:** Current relay path intentionally strips export-only) Tj
T*
(block fields \(tx_list_full, derived counters\) before wire send. If peers still lag, check) Tj
T*
(message-size cap \(ATHO_MAX_MESSAGE_SIZE\) and peer CPU/network limits.) Tj
T*
(- **reorg_depth_exceeded rejects:** A competing branch exceeded policy rollback cap) Tj
T*
(\(max_reorg_depth_blocks\). Review CHECKPOINT_INTERVAL_BLOCKS, MAX_REORG_CHECKPOINT_MULTIPLIER,) Tj
T*
(and MAX_REORG_DEPTH_BLOCKS in Src/Utility/const.py.) Tj
T*
(- **P2P logs are too noisy:** Current defaults keep high-volume tx/inv/getdata lines at DEBUG) Tj
T*
(and dedupe repeated INFO lines.) Tj
T*
(- keep default lightweight mode:) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_NETLOG_LEVEL=INFO) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_NETLOG_DEDUP_SECONDS=45) Tj
T*
(- temporarily increase detail:) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_NETLOG_LEVEL=DEBUG) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_NETLOG_TX_ACTIVITY_INFO=1) Tj
T*
(- send propagation/recovery diagnostics are in:) Tj
T*
(- logs/<network>/api/send_intent_audit.log) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(API / Auth) Tj
T*
(- **401/403 errors:** Missing/invalid X-API-Key/X-User/X-Pass or missing permissions \(e.g.,) Tj
T*
(send_tx, mining\). Check Src/Config/Api_Keys.json; recreate keys with Src/Api/auth.py if needed.) Tj
T*
(- **HMAC failures:** If REQUIRE_HMAC is on, include X-TS and X-Sig for every request; ensure) Tj
T*
(clock skew < ±60s.) Tj
T*
(- **CLI can?t connect:** Verify ATHO_API_URL \(CLI reads Src/Config/NodePorts.json\). If using) Tj
T*
(Docker, use the host-mapped API port from docker compose port.) Tj
T*
(- **HTTP 500 from API:** Often missing deps or missing API key file in container. Rebuild images) Tj
T*
(and ensure Src/Config/Api_Keys.json exists/mounted; check container logs for import errors.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(GUI / Web Explorer) Tj
T*
(- **Request inbox icon appears in wrong place / top-bar alignment looks off**) Tj
T*
(- Cause: stale GUI process or older local GUI file loaded from another path/release folder.) Tj
T*
(- Fix:) Tj
T*
(- fully stop GUI and relaunch from the same repo/venv path,) Tj
T*
(- verify you run Src/GUI/gui.py from this workspace,) Tj
T*
(- if needed clear stale Python caches and restart.) Tj
T*
(- **Clicking inbox does not open request page**) Tj
T*
(- Cause: stale GUI process or feature-disabled runtime.) Tj
T*
(- Fix:) Tj
T*
(- restart GUI from this workspace/venv,) Tj
T*
(- note: current alpha build keeps request inbox UI disabled by default,) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
