(- confirm requests page is present only in builds where it is explicitly enabled,) Tj
T*
(- verify node/API is reachable and authenticated.) Tj
T*
(- **Fund request -> Send security step fails**) Tj
T*
(- Cause: pasted verification address does not exactly match requester address.) Tj
T*
(- Fix:) Tj
T*
(- use Copy Request Address,) Tj
T*
(- paste exact value into verify field,) Tj
T*
(- continue \(send modal prefill opens only on exact match\).) Tj
T*
(- **Explorer popup says it cannot start bridge:** Ensure GUI can read/write) Tj
T*
(Src/GUI/web_explorer.html and that local loopback bind is available \(127.0.0.1\). Restart GUI and) Tj
T*
(try again.) Tj
T*
(- **Explorer opens but stats show -- / no peers/tip hash:** Verify node API is reachable and) Tj
T*
(authenticated by GUI; check /chain/info and /network/node_count from the active API port.) Tj
T*
(- **Address search returns invalid_address:** Explorer accepts Base56 or HPK; verify no) Tj
T*
(whitespace/newlines were copied and network prefix matches the selected chain.) Tj
T*
(- **Explorer page feels stale:** click Refresh in explorer, then refresh node/API state in GUI) Tj
T*
(if local node role changed.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Storage / LMDB) Tj
T*
(- **LMDB file not found / map full:** Ensure storage paths exist; increase map size if needed.) Tj
T*
(Clean start: remove blockchain_storage* if you intend to resync.) Tj
T*
(- **Corruption/stale data after upgrades:** Wipe blockchain_storage* and Peers.json and resync;) Tj
T*
(keep backups before deleting.) Tj
T*
(- **Permission errors on LMDB:** Ensure the process/container user can write to the volume;) Tj
T*
(adjust ownership/permissions on macOS/Linux.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Mining) Tj
T*
(- **Miner mining its own fork:** Bootstrap it to the authoritative node) Tj
T*
(\(ATHO_BOOTSTRAP=<seed>:56000\), align networks, and clear peers/storage if formats changed.) Tj
T*
(- **Reward/balance not showing:** Ensure API auth headers are present; check mempool/UTXO sync;) Tj
T*
(confirm the address mapping \(HPK/Base56\) is correct.) Tj
T*
(- **HTTP 403 on wallet send:** The API key lacks send_tx or password is wrong; recreate key with) Tj
T*
(proper permissions.) Tj
T*
(- **broadcast_rejected: Invalid pubkey: pubkey must use canonical base64 wire encoding:** The) Tj
T*
(node is enforcing canonical witness wire encoding and rejected hex witness payloads. Ensure) Tj
T*
(sender/receiver nodes are on the updated code path and restart wallet/full/miner together.) Tj
T*
(- **block_tx_verify_failed with Fee ... below required minimum ... \(vsize=...\) after mempool) Tj
T*
(accepted:** Usually version skew or stale runtime where one path sizes tx differently. Run one) Tj
T*
(code version across wallet/full/miner, restart all processes, clear stale mempool entries, and) Tj
T*
(retry.) Tj
T*
(- **PoW workers not scaling or unexpectedly single-core:** Check POW_WORKER_CORES,) Tj
T*
(POW_MULTIPROCESS_ENABLED, and POW_WORKER_NONCE_CHUNK in constants/env. If requested cores exceed) Tj
T*
(available CPUs, runtime caps to max CPU count and logs the cap event.) Tj
T*
(- **Miner prints too frequently / console overhead:** raise POW_PROGRESS_INTERVAL_SEC to reduce) Tj
T*
(progress-print I/O.) Tj
T*
(- **Wallet import fails:** The GUI import accepts Atho .txt exports in both current structured) Tj
T*
(format and legacy warning-header format. Duplicates by HPK/Base56 are rejected/skipped. If the) Tj
T*
(identifier already exists but HPK/Base56 is unique, the importer auto-renames to import_#.) Tj
T*
(- **Mnemonic restore mismatch:** Ensure the phrase words and order are exact, and use the same) Tj
T*
(passphrase/account/index used at creation time. A different passphrase/path intentionally) Tj
T*
(derives a different key.) Tj
T*
(- **CLI shows API reported non-canonical recovery mode... after a successful mnemonic recover:**) Tj
T*
ET
